name: Senka Intermediary - Sun Mou
desc:
Your opponent cannot target this card for an attack while you control another "Senka" monster. You can only use each of these effects of "Senka Intermediary - Sun Mou" once per turn.
● You can send 1 card you control or in your hand to the GY; add 1 "Senka" monster from your Deck to your hand, except "Senka Intermediary - Sun Mou".
● If your other "Senka" monster's effect is activated: You can target 1 monster your opponent controls; return that monster to the hand.
